    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it still has that 'new car' feel! It drives like an absolute dream and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for perfection, you\u2019ve found it. Come see for yourself!",
