    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically superlative E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 power plant operates with surgical precision, benefiting from a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite including rod bearing replacement and a dual-VANOS overhaul. Power delivery is immediate via the six individual throttle bodies, channeled through a robust Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis integrity is verified with a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the variable M-differential translates torque to the tarmac without deflection. This example retains its original factory finishes, free from oxidation or mechanical fatigue. A true turnkey collector piece with a transparent service history.",
