    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning enthusiast. The exterior is finished in a flawless coat that glows with a deep, mirror-like shine, completely free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the interior remains pristine; the high-grade leather upholstery is taut and supple, while the dashboard and trim pieces are free of any sun fade or scratches. Under the hood, the engine bay is remarkably clean, reflecting a lifetime of pampered, climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance. Every service has been performed on schedule by certified technicians, and a complete history of records is included to verify its pedigree. Every electronic feature and mechanical component operates with factory-new precision. This is a turn-key investment piece that offers a driving experience indistinguishable from the day it was first delivered. No stories and no excuses\u2014just pure automotive perfection for the buyer who accepts nothing less than the best.",
